    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Collection Sizes",
      "description": "**Metric:** `ai_memory_collection_size`\n**Measures:** Number of memory points in each V2.0 collection\n**Formula:** `max by (collection) (ai_memory_collection_size{...})` (max to avoid double-counting across project labels)\n**Collections:**\n- **code-patterns**: Implementation patterns, error fixes, refactorings\n- **conventions**: Rules, guidelines, ports, naming conventions\n- **discussions**: Decisions, sessions, preferences, messages\n\n**Expected Growth:**\n- code-patterns: Grows with code changes (PostToolUse hooks)\n- conventions: Relatively stable (seeded from templates)\n- discussions: Grows fastest (every user/agent message)\n\n**Current Verified Totals (via Qdrant API):**\n- code-patterns: 339 points\n- conventions: 160 points\n- discussions: 1,942 points",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 10
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max by (collection) (ai_memory_collection_size{collection=~\"code-patterns|conventions|discussions\"})",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{collection}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max",
            "mean"
          ]
        }
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Deduplication Activity (No Duplicates Detected Yet - EXPECTED)",
      "description": "**Metric:** `ai_memory_dedup_matches{action, collection}`\n**Measures:** Deduplication events over time by action (stored vs skipped_duplicate)\n**Formula:** `sum by (action, collection) (ai_memory_dedup_matches{...})`\n\n**Why \"No data\" is NORMAL:**\nThis metric only shows data when duplicate memories are detected. Duplication happens when:\n1. **Hash Match**: Exact same content stored twice (same SHA-256 hash)\n2. **Semantic Match**: Similar content with >0.95 similarity score\n\n**When this will show data:**\n- Storing identical code patterns multiple times\n- Re-capturing same user messages\n- Duplicate API responses or error messages\n\n**Current Status:** No duplicates detected yet - this is GOOD! It means:\n- Content is unique across captures\n- Deduplication system is working (not triggering on unique content)\n- Memory is growing organically without redundancy\n\n**Note:** Code fix deployed (BUG-021) - metric will populate when duplicates occur.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 10
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (action, collection) (ai_memory_dedup_matches{collection=~\"code-patterns|conventions|discussions\"})",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{action}} - {{collection}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "noValue": "No duplicates detected - Memory is unique \u2713"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "sum"
          ],
          "showLegend": true
        }
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 5000,
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
